title: Duke Nukem Zero Hour (First person on Emulator) playthrough -- Part 1
description: After beating Duke Zero Hour on N64 in third person, I decided to try it out on emulator in first person. The framerate is a lot better, and I'm able to play with mouse and keyboard quite well. It feels like a whole different game, and it's fucking sweet!
